---
title: Cannellini Bean Veggie Burger with Sriracha Mayo
description: Who doesn't love a veggie burger? The creamy cannellini beans combined with veggies and hummus make for a veggie burger with great texture and even better flavour. Fast and simple, you'll love this veggie burger recipe!
